2
00:00:00.310 --> 00:00:03.180
Open up the borderless map, then

3
00:00:03.180 --> 00:00:06.380
Head for that unknown edge of the ocean

4
00:00:06.380 --> 00:00:10.770
LET’S SAIL ON right now, hoist your sails up high

5
00:00:10.770 --> 00:00:13.760
Riding on the wind

6
00:00:18.890 --> 00:00:23.100
DON’T GIVE UP, it’s time to finish what we started

7
00:00:23.290 --> 00:00:26.070
So don't you grow disheartened

8
00:00:26.380 --> 00:00:29.830
Laugh the tears away through the storm

9
00:00:30.030 --> 00:00:34.260
SHOUT IT OUT, when you feel down always remember

10
00:00:34.600 --> 00:00:36.860
That’s what your friends are there for

11
00:00:36.890 --> 00:00:39.020
Y’know there’s no point in fronting,

12
00:00:39.020 --> 00:00:42.940
your crew will always have your back

13
00:00:43.310 --> 00:00:47.040
Even in the face of utter darkness

14
00:00:47.270 --> 00:00:50.030
C’mon, BRAVE IT OUT We’ll be alright

15
00:00:50.330 --> 00:00:53.820
Together you know that we’ll never lose a fight

16
00:00:54.040 --> 00:00:56.810
Open up the borderless map, then

17
00:00:56.830 --> 00:00:59.670
Head for that unknown edge of the ocean

18
00:00:59.970 --> 00:01:04.250
All great journeys starts with a single step

19
00:01:04.320 --> 00:01:05.260
DREAMIN’ ON

20
00:01:05.260 --> 00:01:08.040
Open up the borderless map, then

21
00:01:08.040 --> 00:01:10.780
Raise the flag we swore to defend

22
00:01:10.930 --> 00:01:13.670
We’ll never stop until we’ve reached the top

23
00:01:13.740 --> 00:01:18.140
Just be true to yourself until the end

24
00:01:18.270 --> 00:01:22.980
Set sail and grab it, DREAMIN ON

25
00:01:31.900 --> 00:01:34.450
<b>My Bible</b>

26
00:01:34.450 --> 00:01:36.700
Big Sis! Stay with me!

27
00:01:38.130 --> 00:01:39.120
Big Sis!

28
00:01:39.870 --> 00:01:41.580
Hey, dumbasses!

29
00:01:41.580 --> 00:01:43.580
Fetch the medics!

30
00:01:46.450 --> 00:01:47.170
Hey!

31
00:01:47.170 --> 00:01:47.940
Sir!

32
00:01:48.920 --> 00:01:53.890
Find those two, corner them,
then summon the rest of us.

33
00:01:56.850 --> 00:01:59.200
Yamato, you bastard...

34
00:01:59.200 --> 00:02:00.850
Page One!

35
00:02:00.850 --> 00:02:03.510
You took a pretty nasty hit too.

36
00:02:04.490 --> 00:02:06.900
Yeah, that was quite the punch...

37
00:02:06.900 --> 00:02:08.850
Think he dislocated my jaw.

38
00:02:08.850 --> 00:02:10.230
That's all?!

39
00:02:10.650 --> 00:02:13.660
More importantly, where are the medics?

40
00:02:13.660 --> 00:02:15.910
We're here!

41
00:02:26.880 --> 00:02:29.130
You're hurting my eyes!

42
00:02:34.550 --> 00:02:36.760
Pay-Pay!

43
00:02:38.600 --> 00:02:40.560
It hurts ever so much!

44
00:02:40.560 --> 00:02:43.350
Poor sweet little me!

45
00:02:43.350 --> 00:02:45.560
Maybe you should pipe down then?

46
00:02:45.560 --> 00:02:47.390
What did you say?!

47
00:02:47.390 --> 00:02:49.230
Are you trying to make me cry?!

48
00:02:54.530 --> 00:02:56.900
That lousy Yamato!

49
00:02:56.900 --> 00:03:00.910
How dare he steal
Viceroy Kaido's Thunder Bagua?!

50
00:03:00.910 --> 00:03:02.500
She's fine all right.

51
00:03:03.670 --> 00:03:06.040
His is more like Blunder Bagua.

52
00:03:08.640 --> 00:03:12.140
It didn't even hurt...

53
00:03:12.140 --> 00:03:13.460
Big Sis...

54
00:03:13.460 --> 00:03:14.800
Master Page One!

55
00:03:14.800 --> 00:03:17.300
Young Master Yamato
and Straw Hat have stopped!

56
00:03:17.300 --> 00:03:18.340
Okay!

57
00:03:19.780 --> 00:03:21.430
Hey, Pay-Pay!

58
00:03:22.820 --> 00:03:25.810
Don't leave me!

59
00:03:28.600 --> 00:03:30.480
Where are you taking me?!

60
00:03:30.480 --> 00:03:33.070
I don't have time for strangers!

61
00:03:33.070 --> 00:03:34.490
Please wait.

62
00:03:34.490 --> 00:03:36.700
I merely wish to speak.

63
00:03:37.880 --> 00:03:39.440
Get out of my way!

64
00:03:53.770 --> 00:03:55.470
Listen to what I have to say!

65
00:04:09.980 --> 00:04:11.650
You have five seconds!

66
00:04:20.190 --> 00:04:21.620
People can hear us.

67
00:04:21.620 --> 00:04:23.160
Let's speak in private.

68
00:04:24.490 --> 00:04:26.000
Then forget it!

69
00:04:32.250 --> 00:04:34.210
Gum-Gum...

70
00:04:34.210 --> 00:04:36.420
Gatling!

71
00:04:52.090 --> 00:04:53.230
You stubborn jerk!

72
00:04:55.340 --> 00:04:57.690
Red Hawk!

73
00:05:06.820 --> 00:05:08.170
This reminds me of...

74
00:05:09.240 --> 00:05:11.670
my battle against him!

75
00:05:19.050 --> 00:05:20.300
Damn!

76
00:05:20.300 --> 00:05:21.430
They're gone!

77
00:05:21.430 --> 00:05:22.970
What's going on?

78
00:05:22.970 --> 00:05:24.300
Where's Yamato?

79
00:05:24.740 --> 00:05:25.720
I'm sorry!

80
00:05:25.720 --> 00:05:28.020
We lost them both!

81
00:05:29.730 --> 00:05:29.770
<b>Performance

Floor



Skull Dome</b>

82
00:05:29.770 --> 00:05:29.810
<b>Performance

Floor



Skull Dome</b>

83
00:05:29.810 --> 00:05:34.440
<b>Performance

Floor



Skull Dome</b>

84
00:05:35.190 --> 00:05:38.650
The day Kozuki Oden fell...

85
00:05:39.400 --> 00:05:43.910
his stronghold, Oden Castle,
fell alongside him!

86
00:05:44.710 --> 00:05:50.580
However, a group of people inside
the castle vanished into thin air!

87
00:05:51.100 --> 00:05:54.800
Samurai from the Red Scabbards
and this runt!

88
00:05:57.670 --> 00:06:00.550
Where did they disappear to?

89
00:06:02.220 --> 00:06:04.020
To the future!

90
00:06:05.190 --> 00:06:08.970
They crossed through twenty years of time...

91
00:06:08.970 --> 00:06:14.730
resurfacing in the Wano of today!
They haven't aged a day!

92
00:06:16.110 --> 00:06:19.900
And who exactly was responsible
for this sorcery?!

93
00:06:19.900 --> 00:06:22.150
I'll tell you...

94
00:06:22.150 --> 00:06:25.740
None other than Kozuki Toki!

95
00:06:26.280 --> 00:06:31.410
Oden's wife, Toki, was a witch who could
send these malcontents into the future!

96
00:06:35.570 --> 00:06:37.360
No way!

97
00:06:37.360 --> 00:06:41.880
There are brats with topknots all over Wano!

98
00:06:42.590 --> 00:06:46.090
The Kozuki name died out decades ago!

99
00:06:46.090 --> 00:06:47.760
Right, brother?!

100
00:06:51.390 --> 00:06:52.810
Yeah, man!

101
00:06:52.810 --> 00:06:54.850
Y-You're totally right!

102
00:06:57.020 --> 00:06:59.320
Yo, yo, Shogun Orochi!

103
00:06:59.320 --> 00:07:02.190
Don't keep him so far from us!

104
00:07:02.190 --> 00:07:04.650
Bring that brat down here!

105
00:07:04.650 --> 00:07:07.570
I wanna gouge his freakin' eyes out!

106
00:07:08.510 --> 00:07:10.870
How dare you call my mother a witch?!

107
00:07:10.870 --> 00:07:13.620
Y-You will pay for that, Orochi!

108
00:07:14.210 --> 00:07:18.040
Insolent whelp! Don't try to act tough!

109
00:07:18.040 --> 00:07:21.170
How should I execute you?!

110
00:07:21.170 --> 00:07:22.300
Impalement?

111
00:07:22.300 --> 00:07:23.210
Shooting?

112
00:07:23.210 --> 00:07:26.130
Or maybe boiling?!

113
00:07:27.090 --> 00:07:29.470
What should we do, Boss?

114
00:07:29.470 --> 00:07:31.720
I can't stand watching Momo like this!

115
00:07:31.720 --> 00:07:34.310
The samurai will surely act.

116
00:07:34.680 --> 00:07:37.400
Hold fast, Nico Robin!

117
00:07:38.310 --> 00:07:39.770
Lord Momonosuke!

118
00:07:40.190 --> 00:07:41.730
Lord Momonosuke!

119
00:07:41.730 --> 00:07:43.650
Lord Momonosuke!

120
00:07:43.650 --> 00:07:46.000
Lord Momonosuke!

121
00:07:47.840 --> 00:07:51.470
Though frustrated by their inability
to rescue Momonosuke,

122
00:07:51.470 --> 00:07:56.000
the raiding forces have successfully
blended into the banquet!

