00:08:10.850 --> 00:08:13.140
Adjust trim, 38 degrees!

282
00:08:13.510 --> 00:08:15.350
Adjusting, 38 degrees!

283
00:08:16.140 --> 00:08:18.550
Get as close to the island as possible!

284
00:08:18.550 --> 00:08:19.270
Yes, sir!

285
00:08:24.480 --> 00:08:28.070
Strong currents are forming all around us!

286
00:08:40.540 --> 00:08:42.290
It's the same up there.

287
00:08:42.290 --> 00:08:44.750
When we surface, we'll only get one shot!

288
00:08:44.750 --> 00:08:46.130
Understood!

289
00:08:46.530 --> 00:08:49.180
We're counting on you, Traffy!

290
00:08:49.650 --> 00:08:51.970
Bepo! Shachi! Penguin!

291
00:08:51.970 --> 00:08:53.180
Are you ready?!

292
00:08:53.180 --> 00:08:55.520
Aye, aye, Captain!

293
00:08:55.520 --> 00:08:57.020
– Aye, aye, sir!
– Aye, aye, sir!

294
00:08:57.020 --> 00:09:00.820
We're coming for you, Kaido!

295
00:09:02.310 --> 00:09:04.070
All systems clear!

296
00:09:04.070 --> 00:09:05.940
Ready to surface anytime!

297
00:09:07.690 --> 00:09:09.570
Alright! Surface!

298
00:09:32.350 --> 00:09:33.580
It's snowing...?

299
00:09:37.560 --> 00:09:38.680
Room!

300
00:09:54.200 --> 00:09:55.570
Shambles!

301
00:09:57.660 --> 00:09:58.740
They're gone!

302
00:10:00.540 --> 00:10:02.160
Close the door!

303
00:10:02.160 --> 00:10:03.710
We're resubmerging!

304
00:10:03.710 --> 00:10:04.670
Roger!

305
00:10:04.670 --> 00:10:06.450
Rapid descent!

306
00:10:15.260 --> 00:10:16.510
We're here!

307
00:10:16.930 --> 00:10:19.890
That technique of yours is remarkable!

308
00:10:21.760 --> 00:10:23.700
There are two entrances.

309
00:10:23.700 --> 00:10:26.270
No doubt Kaido will be up there.

310
00:10:27.900 --> 00:10:29.020
Hey!

311
00:10:29.020 --> 00:10:31.990
Can't you be a little more gentle?!

312
00:10:31.990 --> 00:10:33.280
You're asking too much!

313
00:10:33.280 --> 00:10:35.660
Whose great idea was this anyway?!

314
00:10:37.030 --> 00:10:38.580
Hey, wait!

315
00:10:39.290 --> 00:10:40.830
That must be...

316
00:10:54.770 --> 00:10:56.680
Ow, ow, ow...

317
00:10:56.680 --> 00:10:59.720
Come on, mew need to be careful!

318
00:10:59.720 --> 00:11:01.520
Nekomamushi!

319
00:11:01.520 --> 00:11:04.310
You have grown much bigger!

320
00:11:05.390 --> 00:11:08.020
Kawamatsu! You're alive!

321
00:11:09.190 --> 00:11:10.230
Ashura!

322
00:11:10.230 --> 00:11:11.980
You made it too!

323
00:11:11.980 --> 00:11:14.110
Yeah, it's been a while!

324
00:11:17.280 --> 00:11:20.280
Marco! You carried him here?!

325
00:11:21.370 --> 00:11:24.580
Carrying two people really takes it out of you!

326
00:11:24.960 --> 00:11:26.000
Two?!

327
00:11:37.700 --> 00:11:39.680
– Izo!
– Izo!

328
00:12:00.990 --> 00:12:02.370
Big Brother...

329
00:12:06.480 --> 00:12:10.380
Big Brother!

330
00:12:14.550 --> 00:12:17.930
Kiku, you have become a fine samurai.

331
00:12:17.930 --> 00:12:19.970
– Izo!
– Izo!

332
00:12:19.970 --> 00:12:22.220
You are a sight for sore eyes!

333
00:12:22.220 --> 00:12:24.180
I am so glad that you came back!

334
00:12:24.850 --> 00:12:28.350
I forgot to mention it before!

335
00:12:28.350 --> 00:12:33.550
Marco said he knew Izo's whereabouts,
so I went there to see him!

336
00:12:33.550 --> 00:12:36.400
Marco! You haven't changed one bit!

337
00:12:36.400 --> 00:12:37.570
You think?

338
00:12:37.570 --> 00:12:40.570
We can reminisce about
the good old days later!

339
00:12:41.820 --> 00:12:46.750
Something on the sea caught my eye earlier,
so I'm gonna go check it out.

340
00:12:50.120 --> 00:12:52.210
Marco! Thank you!

341
00:12:58.880 --> 00:13:01.680
I'm glad I waited for twenty years.

342
00:13:03.090 --> 00:13:06.310
Let's take down Kaido at any cost!

343
00:13:07.640 --> 00:13:10.230
Hey, is Linlin ready yet?!

344
00:13:10.230 --> 00:13:14.570
Oh, Emperor Big Mom is
already on her way here!

345
00:13:15.610 --> 00:13:18.490
You should've told me that, Bao Huang!

346
00:13:19.910 --> 00:13:21.360
My bad!

347
00:13:22.490 --> 00:13:24.240
You can go now.

348
00:13:24.990 --> 00:13:29.370
We'll make our grand announcement
alongside Momonosuke's execution!

349
00:13:30.370 --> 00:13:31.610
Let's go!

350
00:13:39.880 --> 00:13:41.220
All right!

351
00:13:41.220 --> 00:13:44.640
A toast to celebrate this execution!

352
00:13:47.060 --> 00:13:49.600
Oh, Viceroy Kaido?

353
00:14:03.700 --> 00:14:07.370
Here comes Viceroy Kaido!

354
00:14:16.130 --> 00:14:17.800
Listen up!

355
00:14:18.800 --> 00:14:20.460
All you bastards!

356
00:14:21.030 --> 00:14:26.260
Allow me to spice up this brat's dull execution.

357
00:14:29.430 --> 00:14:34.020
This is... the New Onigashima Project!

358
00:14:46.240 --> 00:14:53.370
<b>Castle

Attic</b>

359
00:14:57.030 --> 00:14:58.350
Five minutes!

360
00:15:01.800 --> 00:15:03.420
Years ago...

361
00:15:04.340 --> 00:15:05.500
I told my father...

362
00:15:06.740 --> 00:15:09.100
that I wanted to become Kozuki Oden.

363
00:15:10.100 --> 00:15:10.890
Huh?!

364
00:15:10.890 --> 00:15:13.430
In return, he disciplined me thoroughly.

365
00:15:13.430 --> 00:15:16.350
Why are you telling me this?!

366
00:15:16.350 --> 00:15:18.060
And why now of all times?!

367
00:15:18.760 --> 00:15:22.530
Twenty years ago,
I witnessed Oden's execution...

368
00:15:23.350 --> 00:15:25.110
the Legendary Hour.

369
00:15:26.720 --> 00:15:29.250
As a samurai, he was peerless.

370
00:15:30.220 --> 00:15:31.580
The ones who killed him...

371
00:15:32.240 --> 00:15:34.280
were Orochi and my father...

372
00:15:35.300 --> 00:15:36.670
Kaido!

373
00:15:37.880 --> 00:15:39.170
It was infuriating...!

374
00:15:39.840 --> 00:15:41.630
Yet, above all,

375
00:15:42.130 --> 00:15:45.470
my heart was stirred. My tears flowed freely!

376
00:15:47.840 --> 00:15:51.760
Later, I found this in Kuri.

377
00:15:54.140 --> 00:15:57.100
Kozuki Oden's logbook.

378
00:15:54.140 --> 00:15:56.890
"Oden's Travel Record"

379
00:15:57.640 --> 00:15:59.650
Oh, his journal!

380
00:16:02.900 --> 00:16:05.010
It's my bible!

381
00:16:06.110 --> 00:16:09.820
Not even my father or his crew
know about this journal!

382
00:16:09.820 --> 00:16:14.950
The pages are filled with his heroic tales
and other important tidbits.

383
00:16:15.500 --> 00:16:18.330
Now that the Red Scabbards are dead,

384
00:16:18.330 --> 00:16:20.780
someone has to inherit Oden's will!

385
00:16:22.170 --> 00:16:23.590
That's why...

386
00:16:25.500 --> 00:16:28.130
I'm going to open up this country!

387
00:16:45.740 --> 00:16:46.960
You're...

388
00:16:55.830 --> 00:16:58.620
Allow me to fight alongside you!

389
00:17:03.710 --> 00:17:06.800
You said you were Kaido's son.

390
00:17:08.910 --> 00:17:11.300
Kozuki Oden was a man, correct?

391
00:17:11.300 --> 00:17:13.850
So I became a man, too.

392
00:17:14.810 --> 00:17:17.390
You are incredibly strong.

393
00:17:17.390 --> 00:17:21.020
I could tell you were holding back
when we fought before.

394
00:17:28.280 --> 00:17:30.240
You remind me of Ace.

395
00:17:30.240 --> 00:17:31.320
Wha...?!

396
00:17:39.750 --> 00:17:40.960
Huh?!

